// Caustic light shimmer · 6 SVG marine symbols (no emoji)
// Education: 26ft box truck port work, TWIC card (tsa.gov/twic), liftgate ship ops
// 9 CSS keyframes (am prefix). Coin cursor.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

